https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100054237188521 
 
You will need to wait and be observed for 15 minutes after your vaccination.
 
You must wear a facemask and be prepared to expose your full shoulder and upper arm without removing the facemask.
 
DO NOT ATTEND – PLEASE REBOOK If you are unwell with cold or flu like symptoms, sore throat, cough a high fever etc, have been to any locations of interest, are awaiting a COVID test or have been asked to stay home and self isolate.
